5000|$|Unitatis redintegratio (Latin for [...] "Restoration <b>of</b> unity") is <b>the</b> <b>Second</b> <b>Vatican</b> Council's decree on ecumenism. It {{was passed}} {{by a vote of}} 2,137 to 11 <b>of</b> <b>the</b> bishops assembled, and was promulgated by Pope Paul VI on 21 November 1964.|$|R
